OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,FSouthampton Football Club has been
OL,7,Fexpelled from the Championship Play-
OL,8,Foffs on Saturday after "admitting
OL,9,Fmultiple breaches of EFL Regulations".
OL,11,FThe EFL said the club has received a
OL,12,Ffour-point deduction that will be
OL,13,Fapplied to the 2026/27 Championship
OL,14,Ftable.
OL,16,FSouthampton FC were not only found to
OL,17,Fhave spied on Middlesbrough earlier
OL,18,Fthis month, but also Oxford United in
OL,19,FDecember 2025 and Ipswich Town in
OL,20,FApril 2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
