PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,FThe first incident of spying was in
OL,7,FDecember 2025, shortly after Tonda
OL,8,FEckert became First Team Manager for
OL,9,FSouthampton FC.
OL,11,FThe side now won't be travelling to
OL,12,FWembley this weekend and their hopes
OL,13,Fof promotion to the Premier League
OL,14,Fnext season are over.
OL,16,FMiddlesbrough are now set to take on
OL,17,FHull in Saturday's play-off final
OL,18,Finstead.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,FThe EFL said Southampton FC has a
OL,7,Fright to appeal the Commission's
OL,8,Fdecision and work will take place to
OL,9,Ftry and resolve this by tomorrow
OL,10,F(Wednesday 20 May).
OL,12,FSouthampton FC have since confirmed to
OL,13,Fthe Press Association they will appeal
OL,14,Fthe sanctions.
OL,16,FIt's possible this could result in a
OL,17,Ffurther change to Saturday's fixture.
OL,18,FThe EFL has said a discussion is
OL,19,Ftaking place with all three clubs
OL,20,Fregarding today's decision.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,FThe 'spygate' scandal all started when
OL,7,FMiddlesbrough reported to the EFL that
OL,8,Fa member of Southampton staff had
OL,9,Fspied on a training session on May 7,
OL,10,Fin breach of league rules, with the
OL,11,FEFL charging them the following day.
OL,13,FThe EFL asked an independent
OL,14,Fdisciplinary commission to shorten the
OL,15,Fresponse period from the usual 14
OL,16,Fdays, and to list a hearing "at the
OL,17,Fearliest opportunity".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,FHowever, Southampton insisted the club
OL,7,Fbe given adequate time to review the
OL,8,Fmatter and respond to the charge
OL,9,Fproperly. It also said an internal
OL,10,Freview would be carried out.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the EFL said: "An
OL,13,FIndependent Disciplinary Commission
OL,14,Fhas today expelled Southampton from
OL,15,Fthe Sky Bet Championship Play-Offs
OL,16,Fafter the Club admitted to multiple
OL,17,Fbreaches of EFL Regulations related to
OL,18,Fthe unauthorised filming of other
OL,19,FClubs' training.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"In addition, the Club has received a
OL,7,Ffour-point deduction that will be
OL,8,Fapplied to the 2026/27 Championship
OL,9,Ftable, alongside a reprimand in
OL,10,Frespect of all the charges.
OL,12,F"The effect of today's order is that
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough are reinstated into the
OL,14,F2026 Play-Offs and will proceed to the
OL,15,FPlay-Off Final against Hull City. The
OL,16,Ffinal remains scheduled for Saturday
OL,17,F23 May, with the kick-off time to be
OL,18,Fconfirmed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"Southampton was first charged on
OL,7,FFriday 8 May, with further charges
OL,8,Fissued on Sunday 17 May in relation to
OL,9,Fadditional breaches during the 2025/26
OL,10,Fseason. Those additional charges arose
OL,11,Ffrom matters identified after the
OL,12,Finitial proceedings involving
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough were initiated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"Southampton admitted breaches of
OL,7,FRegulations requiring Clubs to act
OL,8,Fwith the utmost good faith and
OL,9,Fprohibiting the observation of another
OL,10,FClub's training session within 72
OL,11,Fhours of a scheduled match. The
OL,12,Fadmitted breaches concern fixtures
OL,13,Fagainst Oxford United in December
OL,14,F2025, Ipswich Town in April 2026 and
OL,15,FMiddlesbrough in May 2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"Southampton has a right to appeal the
OL,7,FCommission's decision in accordance
OL,8,Fwith EFL Regulations and the parties
OL,9,Fare working to try and resolve any
OL,10,Fappeal on Wednesday 20 May. Subject to
OL,11,Fthe outcome, it could result in a
OL,12,Ffurther change to Saturday's fixture.
OL,14,F"The EFL is now in discussion with all
OL,15,Fthree Clubs regarding the implications
OL,16,Fof today's decision and will make a
OL,17,Ffurther announcement in due course.
OL,19,F"The Commission's full written reasons
OL,20,Fwill also be published in due course."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
