PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,FIn a post on X, Middlesbrough Football
OL,7,FClub said the decision to expel
OL,8,FSouthampton FC from the Championship
OL,9,FPlay-offs "sends out a clear message".
OL,11,FIn a statement, the club said:
OL,12,F"Middlesbrough Football Club welcomes
OL,13,Fthe outcome of today's Disciplinary
OL,14,FCommission hearing.
OL,16,F"We believe this sends out a clear
OL,17,Fmessage for the future of our game
OL,18,Fregarding sporting integrity and
OL,19,Fconduct.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
