PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779286285
OL,3,CSouthampton FC expelled from
OL,4,CChampionship Play-offs after 'spygate'
OL,6,F"As a club, we are now focused on our
OL,7,Fgame against Hull City at Wembley on
OL,8,FSaturday.
OL,10,F"Ticket information for our supporters
OL,11,Fwill be available shortly."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
